{"tid":1513836,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"愛國警察們，請留意《中國公務員法》第54條、納粹德國《軍法》","createTime":"2019-08-28T13:29:33.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:53:34.000Z","uid":48040,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"ebcd47f7dd7346b1268c2d18e942b931a7df3144","tid":1513836,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:29:33.000Z","msg":"《中國公務員法》第54條：<br />\n<br />\n公務員執行公務時，認為上級的決定或者命令有錯誤的，可以向上級提出改正或者撤銷該決定或者命令的意見；上級不改變該決定或者命令，或者要求立即執行的，公務員應當執行該決定或者命令，執行的後果由上級負責，公務員不承擔責任；<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">但是，公務員執行明顯違法的決定或者命令的，應當依法承擔相應的責任。</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.gov.cn/flfg/2005-06/21/content_8249.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gov.cn%2Fflfg%2F2005-06%2F21%2Fcontent_8249.htm&d=EycvRc1shphq9xQQTAPV5IoP%2F%2Fk0CLP%2BSHIq5SsngaE%3D&h=1a1c31ee\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.gov.cn/flfg/2005-06/21/content_8249.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n納粹德國《軍法》：「上級的命令不得成為被告人針對犯罪指控的抗辯理由。」<br />\n<br />\n愛國警察們，我知道和你們講香港法律是沒有用的，因為你們心裡面根本就沒有香港。所以我引用《中國公務員法》以及納粹德國軍法來告誡你們。<br />\n<br />\n歷史終將清算一切，公義必勝！"},{"pid":"72be1c1066daaf07abeed00ca3ac2c4cfda96997","tid":1513836,"uid":198389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-28T13:30:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iLypvE0.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiLypvE0.gif&h=948e64d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5VVVx1d.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5VVVx1d.gif&h=714ea0d2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0CvZfey.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0CvZfey.gif&h=bf891792&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n5QFJ9y.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn5QFJ9y.gif&h=404a1f91&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4KWEZHU.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i